item.title: Boda Tools Box 17″
item.dc:creator: admin
item.description:
• Strong Polypropylene construction.
  • Easy carry handle, which folds back to align with the top of the box.
  • Has 2 top mount transparent spaces for storing small accessories, screws, nails, plugs, bits etc.
  • Two strong latches securely and firmly close the box.
  • Inside the box, it has a removable upper tray for holding small articles.
  • Overall size of the box: 17” (length) x 8.75” (width) x 7.75” (height)
  • Removable tray size: 16” (length) x 7” (width) x 1.80” (depth)
  • Box main compartment size: 16” (length) x 8” (width) x 5.75” (depth)
